Updated kitchen with silestone countertop and newer appliances. Large enclosed porch for entertaining. Short distance to the by by boat from your dock and minutes to Ocean city. Park and community pool within walking distance. HVAC approximately 3 years old as well as newer tile throughout lower level. Lower level has large sliders to open for those breezy nights on the water! Make your dream home on the water a reality today!
